### Welcome to the London Community Fundraising page.
Whether you want to run a marathon, hold a cake sale or jump out of a plane,
there are many ways you can help us to raise vital funds and awareness.
Thiswill help us improve the lives of people with diabetes, and work towards a
future where diabetes can do no harm. Search below and sign up for events
Scratching your head for fundraising ideas? Need some balloons and stickers to
help promote your event? Thinking of hosting a Zoom quiz or games night? We
have lots of hints, tips and fundraising materials to help support your
Do you have a fundraising story to share? We would love to hear from you -
complete our online form to tell us more about you and how you've been
fundraising for us. You can also read stories from amazing fundraisers just
like you, to help you get new ideas and feel inspired.
Whether you need balloons, t-shirts or collection tins or support with your
fundraising we would love to hear from you. Contact us individually, email
